<plot>One fine 2006 morning, a young man wakes up right after sunrise and proceeds outside of his home. His name is Jeff. He knows that its time. So Jeff rides his bicycle over to his friends house. His friend, Ian, agrees to make the movie, even though Jeff has woken him up at five o'clock in the morning. So the two write a movie, and they gather their friends to make it. The only problem, is that one of the friends, Jonathan, thinks the movie is a piece of crap, and refuses to be in it.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?379064</url></doc>
